{"tid":975074,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"擬似2019 ipad mini 5零件照流出，採用A9處理器","createTime":"2019-01-09T10:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:35:33.000Z","uid":100680,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"5c91b11cb3f1349d1545d953e81c0710fbe6c7fe","tid":975074,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"疑似 2019 iPad mini 零件照流出，新款 iPad mini 5採用A9？<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n疑似新款 iPad mini 機殼零件照流出！一位名為「Mr.White」的 Twitter 用戶日前發出了多張照片，包括 iPad mini 的機殼、外觀以及內部零件。由於該用戶爆料的零件不屬於過去的任何一代產品，因此很有可能就是下一代 iPad mini。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n在照片中可以看到 2019 iPad mini 的「玫瑰金」顏色，機殼上方有著圓角的天線，與現有的 iPad mini 設計略有不同；另外現在的顏色也僅有太空灰、金色與銀色，沒有 Twitter 上爆料的玫瑰金。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n除此之外，也可以從新款 iPad mini 的零件中看出下一代的部分規格，包括耳機孔、兩<br />\n個底部喇叭、Lightning 接孔等等。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\nMr.White 也在 Twitter 上發出了宣稱是下一代 iPad mini 的 A9 晶片照。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\niPad mini 5 / 4 A9 Chip <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/7ZGdEhujC6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2F7ZGdEhujC6&d=GVks3%2F%2FXRBcl6rEY6c16IAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0027456f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/7ZGdEhujC6</a><br />\n                                                                                <br />\n&mdash; Mr&middot;white (@laobaiTD) November 17, 2018<br />\n<br />\n現在官網仍在販售的 iPad mini 4 為 2015 年九月發表，至今已經超過兩年未更新；如<br />\n果蘋果沒有放棄此產品線，許多消息都指出今年很有可能推出新款。這次的爆料零件看來<br />\n完成度很高，極有可能就是下一代 iPad mini 將會上市的證據。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\niPad mini 的上市時間過往都落在年底，如果今年沒有特別改變的話，也有可能同樣與年<br />\n底的 iPhone 一起發表。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fjRYIH9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfjRYIH9.png&h=e9fd7d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AgzHwN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAgzHwN9.png&h=721db20a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ags0jQN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fags0jQN.png&h=618d5c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n                                                                                <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DsLtMgPVAAAXhAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDsLtMgPVAAAXhAr.jpg&h=3c9fdf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DsLtMgOUcAARWpY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDsLtMgOUcAARWpY.jpg&h=8f247b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DsLtMgTUwAA0AQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDsLtMgTUwAA0AQg.jpg&h=6b03d4b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77fe20ce15bd98d668de263a0c7778e857e7a54d","tid":975074,"uid":17506,"like":52,"dislike":4,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"A9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e6f790e4a7f3f7745498cc36315e8db387fa7d","tid":975074,"uid":51724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"ipad mini se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa44241074510cbc270fcbae05ca26225839a9","tid":975074,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"幅相似A8多啲喎"},{"pid":"1abe933137d5d3ebe43b9d99445e6d4836e0968a","tid":975074,"uid":100680,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"77fe